==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: oligochaete
<hw>oligochaete</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>Any of an order of
hermaphroditic terrestrial and aquatic annelids (including the
earthworms) having bristles borne singly along the length of the body; a
member of the <ord>Oligochaeta</ord>.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> oligochaete worm.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><ent>oligochaetous</ent>⟦br⟧
